{"tid":374671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都係唔鐘意細路仔，鐘意貓狗多d?","createTime":"2017-08-26T02:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T17:13:01.000Z","uid":84579,"like":98,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ecb4ca51e3199c3c4c61767239b9d83ace4a594","tid":374671,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:50:03.000Z","msg":"D細佬未識講嘢嗰陣就淨係識喊，火車喊，巴士喊，餐廳喊，戲院喊，飛機喊...就算開始大個啲，都好多時仲會喊，有啲開始識講嘢，又以為自己好醒，駁嘴駁舌，講嘢又冇禮貌。有啲人話bb,細路仔好可愛，老實講我連外表都唔覺得佢哋可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係一個低智商同細隻咗少少嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動物就唔得，樣可愛，又識氹人開心，見到佢哋咁得意，會有一種放鬆血壓降低嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且好少動物會係公眾場所嘈，多數都好靜，亦好聽主人話唔會亂跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n附上主人圖數張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/104856_0753dc433c26b162fd4cea17f0e38823.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F104856_0753dc433c26b162fd4cea17f0e38823.jpg&h=0cca44d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/104912_9a58a41418e2e6070cfec7796b7c68c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F104912_9a58a41418e2e6070cfec7796b7c68c5.jpg&h=877340b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/104932_0f0fd83cd4a424739c93e75febff2402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F104932_0f0fd83cd4a424739c93e75febff2402.jpg&h=902b2385&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/104950_8250644a5c831741f22a3990b1ad6a44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F104950_8250644a5c831741f22a3990b1ad6a44.jpg&h=7831ec25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95cd675810d69517e78cc305575da0134bb6c4f7","tid":374671,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914254d42ba4413a9168d086834bbda8a610f1c8","tid":374671,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a01c0fb93e0d89f131a1811b4a1c2cec56d543c","tid":374671,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05573b8355a07c793b43c3e8e25031c21a2f137a","tid":374671,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49f0c0c46fb3848051eccb1f18e5ffcc7601adf","tid":374671,"uid":121349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:49:13.000Z","msg":"想養但養唔"},{"pid":"57db47c09c80d5c70ff001399f225b2ad9116a0a","tid":374671,"uid":121349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:49:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想養但養唔</blockquote><br />\n養唔起"},{"pid":"7c715eb7082bfa4dbbfd60439984d997b0f16804","tid":374671,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/115527_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F115527_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ba4eb479&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"825a62e3927afed5bac23730741739dbc1b159f0","tid":374671,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:58:51.000Z","msg":"利申 bb同貓狗都鐘意"},{"pid":"0d6d41acd5fc94309be8a39059a42b8aa2f6ea24","tid":374671,"uid":42527,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:01:18.000Z","msg":"真係唔太鐵意細路仔 又嘈又煩 又唔知邊到得意<br />\n又要驚佢學壞 做錯事 勁多野煩<br />\n但貓狗就由細到大都好得意 又正 就算做錯事都一樣咁可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfeb37ad02fb968efd760d6f9a6f651eccad9a98","tid":374671,"uid":84579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:33:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係唔太鐵意細路仔 又嘈又煩 又唔知邊到得意<br />\n又要驚佢學壞 做錯事 勁多野煩<br />\n但貓狗就由細到大都好得意 又正 就算做錯事都一樣咁可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger,如果教得唔好/本性差，老咗又會對父母差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貓狗大家都開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eaa5e5377a9a54a22a04fd97c8b4437a29d2d15","tid":374671,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申 bb同貓狗都鐘意</blockquote><br />\nBb真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88607b98d15905c6bf3639d441f5d6fb28cf1bf5","tid":374671,"uid":139282,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"細路真係搞唔撚掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本身有小小對躁音敏感（人為果啲）<br />\n好似特別響嘅咀嚼聲，無意義而重複嘅敲擊我都會好易燥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細路果種高音9叫同爆喊 <br />\n我會想一巴車落去再丟出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：屋企養貓"},{"pid":"33d3415a892add6537ffe60c345b3fb7b64a8484","tid":374671,"uid":84579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細路真係搞唔撚掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本身有小小對躁音敏感（人為果啲）<br />\n好似特別響嘅咀嚼聲，無意義而重複嘅敲擊我都會好易燥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細路果種高音9叫同爆喊 <br />\n我會想一巴車落去再丟出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：屋企養貓</blockquote><br />\n最恐怖係有時突然叫，喺隔離叫分分鐘比佢整到耳鳴，心都離一離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話喺街都好啲，如果係餐廳交通工具坐定定聽佢叫幾個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f45bc7f4b94c59077308b26dfb714684e6d56f","tid":374671,"uid":71133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"係香港細路先咁乞人憎，日本英國個d又可愛又乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a6ab4c2a53270772bd17f48361d7ff5fc64b14","tid":374671,"uid":84579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:45:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港細路先咁乞人憎，日本英國個d又可愛又乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真，係香港支那特別"},{"pid":"5e14c1e96f0eb3d0d533a5d2daa800581816074e","tid":374671,"uid":62269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:00:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港細路先咁乞人憎，日本英國個d又可愛又乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去日本啲細路好多都好乖好靜<br />\n香港嗰啲又嘈又煩 仲要個外表都冇乜吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊忽得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係落街搵隻流浪貓仲得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa94392698c0f0fa76d5b6428e32bafb2a8b92c9","tid":374671,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係香港細路先咁乞人憎，日本英國個d又可愛又乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去日本啲細路好多都好乖好靜<br />\n香港嗰啲又嘈又煩 仲要個外表都冇乜吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊忽得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係落街搵隻流浪貓仲得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個都話似老豆，究竟邊忽似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd98459726e264b386e20e5ec152dec3cf577950","tid":374671,"uid":50870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"此言差矣<br />\n啲細路會咁都係佢地老豆老母唔撚識教啫<br />\n畀我有小朋友一定唔會教成啃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc6c2b067c9fc395c95092e3b997de7fdd7b149","tid":374671,"uid":50870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>此言差矣<br />\n啲細路會咁都係佢地老豆老母唔撚識教啫<br />\n畀我有小朋友一定唔會教成咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"42d22f080c021fda0ab5c001e38fbd94998b45ff","tid":374671,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/115527_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F115527_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ba4eb479&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff78de795b9b2ac652f9bfed4aecc9607ee03552","tid":374671,"uid":10094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:24:23.000Z","msg":"最撚憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee7be449e00498b7f9e0c405cd47b08487de0bc","tid":374671,"uid":35519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.cavemancircus.com//wp-content/uploads/images/2013/august/childfree/childfree_17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cavemancircus.com%2F%2Fwp